ji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T03:26:22.000Z","msg":"佢地已經搶緊愛滋病藥物了"},{"pid":"b872a36a88d1f07a665fdf9cd51a15b02cbc3f04","tid":1863054,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T03:26:40.000Z","msg":"唔怪得雙黃連就有效<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1d1af93ae21d8d94fbe4adb2f6e513140d550d9","tid":1863054,"uid":276524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T03:28:40.000Z","msg":"你覺得如果冇用<br />\n武漢P4會唔會注册使用瑞德西韋於肺炎病人的專利？<br />\n真係多_謝<br />\n以下資訊來自品蔥<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n正傳：<br />\n2019年12月初，不明病因肺炎在武漢爆發<br />\n<a href=\"https://wx1.sinaimg.cn/mw690/482039e5ly1gbikb4s279j21jk3bhu0x.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwx1.sinaimg.cn%2Fmw690%2F482039e5ly1gbikb4s279j21jk3bhu0x.jpg&d=%2FE8yPsxO6SBEJdrny20pcSUaeeTarj8%2BpjPG%2B7PQGFg%3D&h=c1f4e008\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://wx1.sinaimg.cn/mw690/482039e5ly1gbikb4s279j21jk3bhu0x.jpg</a><br />\n前期主要時間點<br />\n<br />\n2020年1月21日，武漢病毒所註冊瑞德西韋治療專利。<br />\n1月27日，美國使用瑞德西韋治療確診病例。<br />\n1月31日，美國發佈病例治療病程、包含糞便陽性等細節<br />\n1月31日，印度學者指2019nCoV顯示出人工合成痕跡，武漢病毒所石正麗「以生命擔保」不是實驗室洩漏<br />\n2月2日，中國藥監局批准瑞德西韋臨床實驗<br />\n2月3日，瑞德西韋於北京機場報關<br />\n2月4日，武漢病毒所宣佈，已經提前搶注專利，併發表了研究論文，論文鏈接：<a href=\"https://www.nature.com/articles/s41422-020-0282-0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nature.com%2Farticles%2Fs41422-020-0282-0&d=%2FE8yPsxO6SBEJdrny20pcSUaeeTarj8%2BpjPG%2B7PQGFg%3D&h=2650103d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nature.com/articles/s41422-020-0282-0</a>"},{"pid":"9b20737d9a67a4efbd7861b450759c60b0307f19","tid":1863054,"uid":27112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T03:31:52.000Z","msg":"大陸死要面，係都要淡化人哋嘅貢獻<br />\n係，隻藥未必百分之百work，但成段嘢丁點appreciate藥廠主動提供協助嘅意思都無，唔好再講乜嘢中國人品德，扮客氣都唔撚識，無家教<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}